item.title: Diamond bought for $13 now worth half a million

item.title: 'Bio' coffin feeds your remains to a tree
Are you having enough sex?
item.description: Of all the things contemporary adults believe are vital for a good marriage, a satisfying sex life and fidelity are often the top two. So it's no wonder that a recent study that reports that American couples in the early 2010s have sex, on average, nine fewer times per year than couples in the 1990s did has set off alarm bells. The decline occurred only among cohabiting or married individuals rather than their single or dating counterparts.
